Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:06.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,High,as high as you can
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.11,0:04:09.57,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All your blood will turn to fountain water
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.61,0:04:13.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're surrounded by plot in this universe
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.09,0:04:16.76,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wash away the stain of blood with tears
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:20.07,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot look,or they will spell on you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:23.52,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wind of fuego will lead us through
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.40,0:04:40.62,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found the light,was real,I am united
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:44.50,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found guide-in line in the raging world
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.54,0:04:48.58,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you see,in the sky,even in this insane world
